					<description><![CDATA[夏季正是水果盛产的季节，天气炎热，多吃一些生津开胃的水果是不错的选择，除了各种瓜果梨桃，李子也是这个时节常见的 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="1">夏季正是水果盛产的季节，天气炎热，多吃一些生津开胃的水果是不错的选择，除了各种瓜果梨桃，李子也是这个时节常见的水果品种之一，相信大家一定不会陌生。作为夏天不可或缺的水果，李子果实饱满圆润，玲珑剔透，微酸的李子含有丰富的维生素C，另外含有其他矿物质、果酸、多种氨基酸、天门冬素以及纤维素等，有利于促进消化和清肝利水。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-215" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/df2cee5029cbd0664777eca334fa7c09.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/df2cee5029cbd0664777eca334fa7c09.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/df2cee5029cbd0664777eca334fa7c09-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/df2cee5029cbd0664777eca334fa7c09-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="2">有些李子直接吃会比较酸，吃两颗牙齿和胃都受不了，可以适当腌制一下，酸酸甜甜又爽口，外面售卖李子加了糖精或添加剂，而且会添加防腐剂。我们还是自己动手腌制吧，比外面买的也健康得多，夏天吃点它超级解暑止渴开胃，无法相容的简单美味。李子的果期很短，一年吃几次就没了，现在正好上市，想吃的快点动手吧。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-216" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/894ed5c22afd0a7125de85890eb5b696.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/894ed5c22afd0a7125de85890eb5b696.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/894ed5c22afd0a7125de85890eb5b696-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/894ed5c22afd0a7125de85890eb5b696-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="3">爽口开胃的腌李子</p>
<p data-track="4">【食材】：李子 1000克、白砂糖 适量、盐 适量、开水 适量</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-217" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e1d03f717961ebb652f5756ea71807ee.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e1d03f717961ebb652f5756ea71807ee.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e1d03f717961ebb652f5756ea71807ee-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e1d03f717961ebb652f5756ea71807ee-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="5">【做法】：1、李子最好挑选翠绿颜色的，这样子最后浸泡出来才脆爽。李子放两勺盐，泡盐水里十分钟，然后清洗干净；</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-218" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e38ed6b2f8b80fa1340fd8d0bdcb2d1d.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e38ed6b2f8b80fa1340fd8d0bdcb2d1d.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e38ed6b2f8b80fa1340fd8d0bdcb2d1d-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e38ed6b2f8b80fa1340fd8d0bdcb2d1d-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">2、起锅烧水，然后倒入开水淹没李子，浸泡大概五分钟，你会发现李子颜色慢慢变黄，用开水浸泡可以去除部分李子的苦涩味，如果不介意酸涩也可以不焯水。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-219" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aac6b1325355dc0fbb8fb7ecbadfcb7a.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aac6b1325355dc0fbb8fb7ecbadfcb7a.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aac6b1325355dc0fbb8fb7ecbadfcb7a-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/aac6b1325355dc0fbb8fb7ecbadfcb7a-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="7">3、李子浸泡好后控干水，每一颗都切5刀左右，这样子方便入味；</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-220" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54e964ffc0f2498f6c1af627394370cb.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54e964ffc0f2498f6c1af627394370cb.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54e964ffc0f2498f6c1af627394370cb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/54e964ffc0f2498f6c1af627394370cb-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="8">4、李子放入用来腌制的玻璃容器，一层李子一层白糖这样让李子全部沾上白糖（可以倒入一小勺开水，促进糖分的融化），想甜点加点糖，想辣加多点辣椒粉腌，然后密封起来放在冰箱冷藏三到五天，随着时间的推移，李子和糖混合一起后会出水，原先酸涩的小李子就变的微酸偏甜而爽口了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-221" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/143a4fa123d7a7645b7c017588f0a138.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/143a4fa123d7a7645b7c017588f0a138.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/143a4fa123d7a7645b7c017588f0a138-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/143a4fa123d7a7645b7c017588f0a138-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9">腌的时间越久越入味，这是腌半个月的李子，表皮已经出现皱褶，色泽更均匀、深润，味道也更柔和啦！</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-222" src="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/94eea57ccc122ac2d3fa481fef98e8d6.jpg" width="936" height="624" alt="6月这水果大量上市，腌一下风味更佳，酸甜爽脆又开胃，流口水了" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/94eea57ccc122ac2d3fa481fef98e8d6.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/94eea57ccc122ac2d3fa481fef98e8d6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/94eea57ccc122ac2d3fa481fef98e8d6-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="10">【小提示】：</p>
<p data-track="11">1、腌李子一定要选绿色硬点，红了的李子口感就是软的</p>
<p data-track="12">2、腌李子虽好吃，但应食之有度，不宜过多食用，吃多了口腔便会形成酸性环境，易损害牙齿。</p>
